{"lemma":"لِصّ","slug":"لِصّ","root":"ل.ص.ص","root_slug":"ل-ص-ص","root_link":"/words/roots/ل-ص-ص","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":5,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":12},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n37728","n37730","n37731"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%84%D9%90%D8%B5%D9%91"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"thief, robber","examples":[{"text":"مَكَانَكَ أَيُّهَا ٱللِّصُّ!","english":"Stop there, thief!"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"thief","tags":["obsolete"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to steal","tags":["obsolete","transitive"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to do secretly","tags":["obsolete","transitive"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to close (the door)","tags":["obsolete","transitive"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be a thief, to be thievish, to steal repeatedly"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to have teeth close together"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to have hunched shoulders, to stoop (of a person or horse)"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to have one's thighs close together (of a woman)"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be narrow (of one's forehead)"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to have unevenly oriented horns (of a sheep)"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of لَصَّ (laṣṣa, “to steal, to do secretly, to close (the door)”) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb","obsolete","transitive"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Borrowed from Ancient Greek λῃστής (lēistḗs)."},"ipa":["/lisˤsˤ/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n37728","headword_ar":"لَصَّ","root":"lS","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He thieved,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stole:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A:) [see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"luSuwSiy~apN","text_ar":"لُصُوصِيَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and the other nouns mentioned therewith, some of which, if not all, are app. inf. ns. of this verb:] and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tlS~S","text_ar":"تلصّص","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same; or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he was thievish:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * Msb, * TA:) [or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he practised theft:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he thieved,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stole, repeatedly:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he acted as a spy;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tajas~asa","text_ar":"تَجَسَّسَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laS~a Al$~aYo'a","text_ar":"لَصَّ الشَّىْءَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, TK,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laS~N","text_ar":"لَصٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A, Msb, K,) [in the CK"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"liS~N","text_ar":"لِصٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":",]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He stole the thing:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) [and]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he did the thing secretly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"covertly."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, K.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laS~a baAbahu","text_ar":"لَصَّ بَابَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laS~N","text_ar":"لَصٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He closed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"locked, his door;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^agolaqahu","text_ar":"اَغْلَقَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aTobaqahu","text_ar":"اَطْبَقَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (A, K, TA;) as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raS~ahu","text_ar":"رَصَّهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laS~a","text_ar":"لَصَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [app. in the sec. pers."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laSiSota","text_ar":"لَصِصْتَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yalaS~u","text_ar":"يَلَصُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laSaSN","text_ar":"لَصَصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His teeth"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aDoraAs","text_ar":"اَضْرَاس"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"were near together, so that no interstice was seen between them."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, TA.) [This verb probably has all the significations indicated by the explanations of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laSaSN","text_ar":"لَصَصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"below.]"}],"source_refs":["A","TA","Msb","TK","K"]},{"entry_id":"n37730","headword_ar":"لِصٌّ","root":"lS","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, A, Msb, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"luS~N","text_ar":"لُصٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, Msb, K,) the latter mentioned by As, (Msb,) but only the former known to Sb, (M,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laS~N","text_ar":"لَصٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (IDrd, A, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A thief; a robber;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, A, Msb, K;) as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laSotN","text_ar":"لَصْتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"t","text_ar":"ت"},{"kind":"text","text":"substituted for the [second]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"S","text_ar":"ص"},{"kind":"text","text":", and the form of the word changed because of the substitution, or it is a dial. form of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"liS~N","text_ar":"لِصٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and is said by Lh to be of the dial. of Teiyi and of some of the Ansár, and also pronounced"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"liSotN","text_ar":"لِصْتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"luSotN","text_ar":"لُصْتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K, art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lSt","text_ar":"لصت"},{"kind":"text","text":":) fem."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"liS~apN","text_ar":"لِصَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laS~apN","text_ar":"لَصَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (A, K:) pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"liS~N","text_ar":"لِصٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"luS~N","text_ar":"لُصٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IDrd, S, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laS~N","text_ar":"لَصٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (IDrd, K,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"luSuwSN","text_ar":"لُصُوصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (IDrd, S, M, Msb, K,) and of the first,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"liSaSapN","text_ar":"لِصَصَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (IDrd, TA,) and of the first (M, TA) and second, (M,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"liSaASN","text_ar":"لِصَاصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, TA,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aloSaASN","text_ar":"اَلْصَاصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":":"},{"kind":"page_break","n":2660},{"kind":"text","text":"(K) [and in the TA said to be so in the T: but this is probably a mistake for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"liSaASN","text_ar":"لِصَاصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": for ISd says,] the word has no pl. of pauc.: (M:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"malaS~apN","text_ar":"مَلَصَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a quasi-pl. n.: (IJ, M:) the pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"liS~apN","text_ar":"لِصَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laS~apN","text_ar":"لَصَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"liS~aAtN","text_ar":"لِصَّاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laS~aAtN","text_ar":"لَصَّاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laSaAy^iSu","text_ar":"لَصَايِصُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, K,) which last is extr. [with respect to rule]: (M:) and the pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"liSotN","text_ar":"لِصْتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"luSuwtN","text_ar":"لُصُوتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (M.)"}],"source_refs":["S","M","A","Msb","K","IDrd","TA","IJ"]},{"entry_id":"n37731","headword_ar":"لَصٌّ","root":"lS","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"luS~N","text_ar":"لُصٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"liS~N","text_ar":"لِصٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}